                        <h5 class="fw-bold">Bespoke Menu Planning</h5>
                        <p class="small text-muted">Custom-designed menus tailored to your cultural preferences and dietary requirements.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="d-flex align-items-start mt-3">
                    <i class="fas fa-seedling mt-1 me-3 text-success"></i>
                    <div>
